{"id": "1513917068511281273", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1126482815610011721", "author_name": "anonymous.409", "author_bot": false, "content": "5枚連続で送ると相変わらずスパム扱いされます笑", "timestamp": "2026-06-09T14:45:56.352000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🙏", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1513917067332686048", "filename": "IMG_0585.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 450312, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1513917067332686048/IMG_0585.png?ex=6a3404a4&is=6a32b324&hm=8910e1efb96643abf66979bd626f6998d229b6e7351d522c675e18851b43bd23&"}, {"id": "1513917068070748331", "filename": "IMG_0586.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 476083, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1513917068070748331/IMG_0586.png?ex=6a3404a4&is=6a32b324&hm=6201a303912b921ad63a8413adf289899cbc25308921e93abbd0d0d31724c985&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1513917782469640263", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "1126482815610011721", "author_name": "anonymous.409", "author_bot": false, "content": "今いるメンツだと､沙耶,ナウティラ,ファイント,ラモンナの反撃パが安定すると思われます｡\nワンダのキーオーダーが相性良いので､取れるなら取りましょう👍 \n立ち回り的には､ファイントのカードをコピーする形になると思います｡", "timestamp": "2026-06-09T14:48:46.573000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["923555882904739850"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1513912038911381645", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1513927118176649216", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "1255343591933476987", "author_name": "n_gm0803", "author_bot": false, "content": "ありがとうございます🙏\nジェンキン引いてきました🫡\n残りの枠は編成出来るなら好み子って感じですよね？\n⑤は救援完凸サルバドル様枠は全力おんぶで①〜④で余った子集める感じでよかったですかね？\nざっくり、こんな感じでしょうか？", "timestamp": "2026-06-09T15:25:52.379000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1126482815610011721"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1513927117878984804", "filename": "IMG_1778.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 368962, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1513927117878984804/IMG_1778.jpg?ex=6a340e00&is=6a32bc80&hm=68c1935efb9ad4154c83bbe0b4409d624f2acdc0a371a7343e8db663410492d2&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1513916462656520282", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1513937161819390142", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "1126482815610011721", "author_name": "anonymous.409", "author_bot": false, "content": "はい👍\n大体そんな感じで行けると思います｡\n一応､1波と3波は精鋭戦がなく､精鋭討伐時のカーニバルバフ(ダメージ強化100%)の恩恵を受けられないので､ダメージ強化の札を優先してつけた方が良いとかはありますが､既に十分形になっているので､後は実際に戦ってみて手持ちを見ながら調整していくという感じで問題ないと思いますね〜", "timestamp": "2026-06-09T16:05:46.970000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-09T16:06:32.577000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1255343591933476987"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🙏", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1513927118176649216", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1513938639460110446", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "1255343591933476987", "author_name": "n_gm0803", "author_bot": false, "content": "素材が足らずレベルがあまり上げれないですが、使って調整してみます。\n夜分にほんとありがとうございます🙏", "timestamp": "2026-06-09T16:11:39.267000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1126482815610011721"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1513937161819390142", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1513939605282361576", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "809817402287718421", "author_name": "neco9900", "author_bot": false, "content": "沙耶の唄コラボ発見して始めた初心者です、よろしくお願いします。", "timestamp": "2026-06-09T16:15:29.537000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1513939746777206875", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1126482815610011721", "author_name": "anonymous.409", "author_bot": false, "content": "カードの強化はトゥルーの号令､ミリアムの3コス､ジェンキンの突撃､ファイントのスキル両方､これらの優先度が特に高い感じです｡\n素材が厳しそうであれば､ここら辺を優先して上げましょう👍\n同様に､キャラ本体のレベルも､その編成の核となるトゥルー､ジェンキン､ファイント辺りを優先してあげましょう！", "timestamp": "2026-06-09T16:16:03.272000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-09T16:18:19.650000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🙏", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1513941467033239737", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1255343591933476987", "author_name": "n_gm0803", "author_bot": false, "content": "優先まで女神！！\nありがとうございます🙏\nパーティの軸になる子を強化して祭り上げて殴る！感じですね！\n期間内に一級警戒は倒せる様に頑張ってみます🌊", "timestamp": "2026-06-09T16:22:53.413000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
