{"id": "1514054523092603010", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "923555882904739850", "author_name": "86_ho_c", "author_bot": false, "content": "ありがとうございます！\nモチーフ札と4章完走頑張ります！", "timestamp": "2026-06-09T23:52:08.078000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1126482815610011721"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1513917782469640263", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1513801127181680770", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064117001892663384", "author_name": "sou84b65", "author_bot": false, "content": "コンティニューを使ってなんとか3-13がクリアできました。\nアドバイスありがとうございました", "timestamp": "2026-06-09T07:05:13.785000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍵", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1513824798696931348", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "638277565252894720", "author_name": "guki.", "author_bot": false, "content": "すみません。\n一応、確認したいんですが\nトゥルーの深淵号令って\n触手で殴ってますが\nこの触手ってトゥルーの\nクリ率とかクリダメの補正乗りますか？\nトゥルーの密約宴で\nクリ率>クリダメ>ダメ強化>狂気増>界域知識\nの優先度で厳選してるんですが", "timestamp": "2026-06-09T08:39:17.514000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1513825820978839673", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "触手はキャラが殴っているのではなく、触手が殴っている判定になるので、本人のバフ系が直接乗ることはありません。", "timestamp": "2026-06-09T08:43:21.245000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1513824798696931348", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1513826075380289598", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "触手は特殊仕様で、チーム内のバフ、クリティカル率、クリティカルダメージを平均化した数値を持つので、全体強化以外は効率がガタ落ちします。", "timestamp": "2026-06-09T08:44:21.899000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1513827309344395314", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "そのため、お伝えするのは心苦しいですが、密約自体の変更をオススメします。\nオススメのセットは、機神降臨、双子黒、深海航路、キーチャ系のいずれかです。\nサブステータスは、\n［部位］\nⅠ:キーチャ Ⅱ:自由 Ⅲ:ダメ強\nⅣ:キーチャⅤ:キーチャ Ⅵ:ダメ強\n[転写]\nキーチャ>ダメ強=狂気増加>その他\nあたりをオススメしておきますー。", "timestamp": "2026-06-09T08:49:16.099000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1513827996132442323", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "638277565252894720", "author_name": "guki.", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@516998769888329749> \nオーマイガー😱\n回答ありがとうございます。\n改善案も頂き感謝です。\n意見については全然気にしません。\nありがとうございました。", "timestamp": "2026-06-09T08:51:59.842000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["516998769888329749"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1513828341008957532", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "ちなみに書き忘れなのですが、ダメージ強化も乗りが悪いです。\nトゥルー解放などで盛った触腕ダメージ上昇、力などで増えた分の数値にはバフしないのです。", "timestamp": "2026-06-09T08:53:22.067000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-09T08:53:31.566000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1513827996132442323", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1513828828026245211", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "638277565252894720", "author_name": "guki.", "author_bot": false, "content": "トゥルーなどの深淵アタッカーは例外として\n基本的にアタッカーは\nやっぱりクリ率とクリダメが優先ですかね", "timestamp": "2026-06-09T08:55:18.181000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1513828899446980770", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2026-06-09T08:55:35.209000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1513828899132276826", "filename": "Screenshot_20260608-0754562.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 106473, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1513828899132276826/Screenshot_20260608-0754562.png?ex=6a33b287&is=6a326107&hm=cbcb7582d4ad6c58428b58b6cfd2681915b89460311262ca9ca3b2b3ac5477fb&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1513828911669313678", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "こんな感じですね", "timestamp": "2026-06-09T08:55:38.123000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
